# Rosa Development Focus

## Primary Development Area
- **ALL future development**: `Rosa_custom_backend/` ONLY
- **Reference patterns**: `examples/` folders are READ-ONLY reference material
- **Never modify**: Any files outside Rosa_custom_backend/

## Architecture Pattern
- **Frontend**: Rosa_custom_backend/src/ (React + TypeScript + Tavus CVI)
- **Backend**: Rosa_custom_backend/backend/ (Python Agent1.py + FastAPI)
- **Split-Screen UI**: Avatar (left) + Dynamic content (right)
- **Function Calls**: Python backend handles ALL complex logic

## Copy Working Patterns From Examples
- **Tavus CVI**: `examples/cvi-ui-conversation/src/components/cvi/`
- **Function Calling**: `examples/cvi-ui-conversation/src/components/CTBTOHandler.tsx`
- **Backend Structure**: `examples/cvi-ui-conversation/backend/Agent1.py`
- **Split-Screen**: `examples/cvi-ui-conversation/src/components/RosaDemo.tsx`

## Development Commands
```bash
cd Rosa_custom_backend
bun install
bun dev
```

